{"tid":1505794,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"戴緊全面罩6800 & 近視入嚟睇睇","createTime":"2019-08-25T15:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T21:37:59.000Z","uid":79228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"edcecac1f0b8a8a1121e2d4bf5e5b0e276c942b2","tid":1505794,"uid":79228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:39:28.000Z","msg":"你需要：<br />\n1.文具鋪Blu tack<br />\n2.爛咗都唔嬲嘅眼鏡，用你嘅方法整走兩邊掛耳<br />\n3.3M 6800面罩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4EN1Vrw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4EN1Vrw.png&h=c6872036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CxBRydc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCxBRydc.png&h=5c31552d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3u5VZTc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3u5VZTc.png&h=9b22e5ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n舊Blu tack要大舊啲同墊高啲，但唔好同塊面有接觸，萬一中彈你希望係包住塊面嘅邊位食力<br />\n調較要無限耐性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋始終同隻眼有多少少距離，所以太深度數未必適合，如果試完會暈或者睇嘢變形太勁就唔適合<br />\n暫時未落場試（主要係長時間固定問題），如果有其他固定方法分享吓（3M隻眼鏡KIT貴到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"014475379cfaa855583069eb2bd3409e8019220d","tid":1505794,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:40:43.000Z","msg":"【置頂】828 metoo集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505524</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e6d867237a962a29eb104e6db4caabc636741d8d","tid":1505794,"uid":249480,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:02:43.000Z","msg":"戴全面既話會唔會戴con好啲"},{"pid":"273d50574e552298d2f549bc72591912ead9d874","tid":1505794,"uid":79228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid